      About this item

      • 【Adjustable Brightness&Color Temperature】 Glow all around lightes, white light 3000K / natural light 4000K / cold light 6500K, high waterproof light strip, high color rendering, true presentation of facial makeup. Side panel ambient light design, long press to adjust brightness, soft light, creating a quiet space, energy saving and durable life.
      • 【Copper-free HD Silver Mirror】 Compliance with US standards. The corner is arc angle, mirror coated with silver nitrate, which is not easy to oxidize and rust. Copper-free environmental protection mirrors that are not prone to blackening are more durable and healthy.
      • 【Heat Control Defogging】 Collecting opinions from most ladies, we learned that the defogging function of mirrors is essential in humid environments. If you choose our anti-fog bathroom mirror, you don't worry about this problem, when you touch the switch button, the anti-fog function will be activated when open second touch mark. Reject water stains on the mirror surface, leaving the mirror refreshed and clear.
      • 【Built-in 360° Bluetooth Speaker】 The hidden Bluetooth on the back of the mirror makes the mirror more concise. Omnidirectional sound technology can ensure its sound spreads evenly. Bring unimaginable 360° sound experience. It can be switched on and off individually.
      • 【Easy to Install】 It can be mounted on the wall as a wall-mounted mirror, all installation accessories and installation instructions are included in the package. Pls note it is plug in. For safety reasons, we strongly recommend a professional electrician to install this product if you want to connect directly to the power cord.
      • 【Satisfaction Service】 24 Monthes Service. We reinforced the cardboard boxes, and there are multi warehouses in US for us, the orders are shipped nearby. Any problem, pls feel free to let us know and we will help you solve the problem within 24 H.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
